Godimo ga lenaneo la poloko ya Dr Mathume ‘Bra Knox’ Bopape go be go ngwadilwe, ka mangwalo a magolo ka mathoko a sefahlego sa gagwe: ‘KETEKO YA BOPHELO’. Tirelo ya poloko e be e kwagala kudu bjalo ka mokete esego sello. Ba lapa, bao a šomilego naye le bao ba mo tsebago ba ba be ba kwana ka taba e tee – yo e be e le monna yo boleta, wa tlhompho wa go rata batho le gona wa go ba le serithi. Le ge ka seemo e be e le motho wa go ema ka maoto, wa go kgwahla, go ela ga sefahlego sa gagwe le monywanywo di be di apeša motho ka borutho le pholo moyeng. E be e le motho wa Kgoobe.

Mohu Mathume, yo a belegwego ka 1949, o phethile dithuto tša motheo gagabo ka 1961 Sekolong sa Praemari sa Kgokong. Go tloga fao o ile a fetela Sekolong seo se Phagamego sa Hwiti fao a feditšego marematlou ka 1967. Nakong yeo bokgoni bja gagwe bja Mmetse bo be bo šetše bo le pepeneneng. O phethile dithuto tša Diploma ya Borutiši ka 1970 Yunibesithing ya Limpopo (Leboa). Yona e latetšwe ke tikrii ya BSc (Unisa) ka 1977 fao dithutokgolo tša gagwe e bego e le Operations Research, Information Systems le Mathematical Statistics. Ka 1985 o phethile tikrii ya Hons.BSc (Unisa) fao dithuto tša gagwe e bego e le Dynamic Programming, Integer Programming le Advanced Linear Programming. O phethile tikrii ya MSc ka 1989 (University of London) fao a dirilego dithuto tša Mathematics, Statistical and Computing Education fao hlogo ya diphatišišo tša gagwe e bego e le ‘A Similar Triangles Microworld’. Molaodi yo, o phethile dithuto tša bongaka, PhD ka 2002 (Aalborg University – Denmark) fao diphatišišo tša gagwe di bego di šeditše ‘School-Based Mathematics INSET.

Mohu Mathume o phatlaladitše pampiri ya Mmetse, ‘Logo and Geometry Teaching’ go tšenale ya Pythagoras No.25, 25 April 1991. Gape ke yo mongwe wa bangwadi go dipuku tšeo di latelago tša Mmetse: Understanding Mathematics Grade 4 (1993); Grade 5 (1994; Grade 6 (1997); Grade 7 (1999); Grade 9 (2001); Grade 10 (2002); New Understanding Numeracy, Grades 1 – 3 (2003); New Day by Day Numeracy, Grades 1 – 3 (2003); New Understanding Mathematics, Grades 4 – 6 (2004); New Day by Day Mathematics, Grades 4 – 6 (2004).

Mohu Mathume o bile morutiši mengwaga e selelago pele a hlatlošetšwa go ba motlatšahlogo mengwaga e mebedi pele a ebaHlogo ya Sekolo sa Leolo mengwaga e meraro. Go tloga fao o bile Hlogo ya Lefapa la Saense Kholetšheng ya Mokopane ka 1983 – 1984. O bile Moeletši wa Thuto ya Mmetse maemong a go fetana (1985 – 1994). Ngwageng wa 1995 o šomile National Productivity Institute bjalo ka Setsebi (Consultant). O bile Molaodi le Mohlahlobiomogolo go Kgoro ya Thuto ya Limpopo mengwageng ya 1994 – 1997. Ka 1997- 2003 o bile Hlogo (Rector) ya Kholetšhe ya Mmetse le Saense ya MASTEC mola a be a šoma gape bjalo ka Mokgokaganyi le Molaodi wa Projeke ya mananeo a bosetšhaba a thuto ya Mmetse. Go tlogeng fa, Mohu Mathume o ile a thwalwa Yunibesithing ya KwaZulu-Natal bjalo ka Molaodi wa ‘Centre for Advancement for Science and Mathematics Education. Ge a tlogela modiro ka lebaka la bolwetši, o be a le maemong a.

